FAQ

Can I still use Wix in my classroom if I use my own curriculum materials?

Yes! Wix is an open platform. We encourage educators to get creative in bringing all of our products into the classroom.

Who do I contact if my student is having trouble with their account?

For student project related inquiries, you can contact highered@wix.com directly. For questions about your account access or subscription, please use Wix's customer support line.

Does Wix still offer private classroom instruction?

Due to current influx in demand, we vet classroom visit requests on a case by case basis. Contact highered@wix.com if you have a non-traditional request.

Where can I learn more about Base44, the newest company acquired by Wix?

To learn more about Base44 opportunities in the classroom, email elsa@base44.com.
